mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Datebook", "On the Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Area Publications", "The Walkthru", "Dialog for Callers", "National Convention", "Ladies on the Square", "Picture Story", "Phrasing by Terry Golden", "Style Series", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Fred Staeben", "Paging the Roundancers: Opal & Chuck Goodman", "Current Best Sellers", and "Experimental Lab".
